Lagoon AI - Intelligent Chatbot
Lagoon AI is a lightweight and powerful chatbot that leverages cutting-edge AI models to generate human-like responses. Built using Flask (Python) for the backend and React.js for the frontend, this chatbot interacts seamlessly with users by integrating APIs from Hugging Face, DeepSeek, or other AI providers.

🚀 Features
✅ AI-Powered Conversations – Supports various AI models like Gemma, Mistral, and more
✅ REST API Integration – Uses Hugging Face API for intelligent responses
✅ Simple & Interactive UI – Built with React.js for a smooth user experience
✅ Customizable & Scalable – Easily swap AI models or expand functionality
✅ Secure API Key Handling – Uses a .env file for better security

🛠️ Tech Stack
Backend: Flask (Python)

Frontend: React.js

API Integration: Hugging Face Inference API

Environment Management: .env file for API keys

